<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM9.9">
<l>muṉṉorunāḷ maḻuvāḷi cilaivāṅki yavaṉṟavattai muṟṟuñ ceṟṟāy</l>
<l>uṉṉaiyumuṉ ṉarumaiyaiyu muṉmōyiṉ varuttamumoṉ ṟākak koḷḷā</l>
<l>teṉṉaiyumeṉ meyyuraiyu meyyākak koṇṭuvaṉam pukka ventāy</l>
<l>niṉṉaiyē makaṉākap peṟappeṟuvē ṉēḻpiṟappu neṭuntōḷ vēntē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who, having once obtained the bow from the axe-wielder,</l>
<l rend="indent">completely destroyed that one’s tapas</l>
<l>O my Father who entered the forest taking me and my promise to be the truth,</l>
<l rend="indent">without considering as worthy of regard Yourself,</l>
<l rend="indent">or the difficulty [we had in] obtaining You  or Your mother’s suffering!</l>
<l>O long-armed King! I shall get to beget Yourself as [my] son for all seven births [to come]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
